data.description: Discover this charming two-story home just minutes from Ft. Bragg, shopping, and dining. This home boasts formal living and dining rooms. A sleek kitchen with stainless appliances, beautiful backsplash, plenty of counter space and ample storage. Home features three spacious bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms and single car garage. Enjoy a fenced yard for relaxation and play. Nestled on a quiet dead-end road in an established neighborhood, there's abundant space for indoor and outdoor entertaining. Sellers are offering buyers a $1,000 allowance paid at closing to a contractor of their choice in lieu of repairs. Don't miss out on this opportunity – your search is over. Welcome Home! AGENTS-NOT member of MLS? Call Showing Time. Let them know you are NOT a member and need access and or disclosures/supporting docs.
